- Did you make that yourself?
- Well of course.

1091
01:35:15,712 --> 01:35:17,632
Wanted to produce an impression.

1092
01:35:18,793 --> 01:35:20,273
And you succeeded.

1093
01:35:22,632 --> 01:35:25,672
I mean to say, I am a gourmet.

1094
01:35:26,312 --> 01:35:28,671
And I hate to cook.

1095
01:35:29,512 --> 01:35:33,790
With my lazy-bones I hardly have
any time for cooking anyway.

1096
01:35:36,431 --> 01:35:38,471
- You teach them?
- Yes.

1097
01:35:40,551 --> 01:35:42,590
