1098
01:35:45,310 --> 01:35:48,871
I try to teach them to think.

1099
01:35:49,830 --> 01:35:51,630
If at least a little.

1100
01:35:53,230 --> 01:35:56,230
And have a personal opinion
about everything.

1101
01:35:57,629 --> 01:36:00,349
- Can I have some more?
- Of course.

1102
01:36:02,629 --> 01:36:07,349
- What do they teach you?
- I guess, the same thing.

1103
01:36:11,109 --> 01:36:15,068
This is not fish.
This is anything but fish in aspic.

1104
01:36:15,629 --> 01:36:19,509
This is... It needs some
horse-radish to go with.

1105
01:36:21,228 --> 01:36:26,228
And I represent the most
conservative of all professions.

1106
01:36:31,748 --> 01:36:33,867
We can compete there.

1107
01:36:34,107 --> 01:36:35,468
No, I'm serious.

1108
01:36:36,107 --> 01:36:39,907
With us it is dangerous
to have a personal opinion.

1109
01:36:40,147 --> 01:36:42,147
What if it's a wrong one?

1110
01:36:43,427 --> 01:36:46,467
Doctors' mistakes
are extremely costly.

1111
01:36:47,386 --> 01:36:51,667
Teachers' mistakes
are not that obvious,

1112
01:36:52,946 --> 01:36:57,866
But in the end
they are no less costly.

1113
01:36:59,385 --> 01:37:00,946
Maybe you're right.

1114
01:37:01,186 --> 01:37:04,025
Still you and me have the most

1115
01:37:04,786 --> 01:37:07,625
wonderful and the most needed jobs
in the world.

1116
01:37:07,945 --> 01:37:09,624
Not judging by the salaries.

1117
01:37:12,504 --> 01:37:14,225
That's right.

1118
01:37:16,865 --> 01:37:21,024
When your friends were saying
all these good things about you,

1119
01:37:22,625 --> 01:37:25,623
God knows why I felt proud.

1120
01:37:28,464 --> 01:37:29,943
No use wheedling.

1121
01:37:31,904 --> 01:37:35,503
By the way, unlike you,
your friend noticed,

1122
01:37:35,744 --> 01:37:37,863
That I'm a reliable serious person.

1123
01:37:38,103 --> 01:37:40,103
You didn't break into her house.

1124
01:37:42,503 --> 01:37:46,742
That's true,
I didn't break into her house yet.

1125
01:37:54,023 --> 01:37:58,022
What an unusual way
to see in the New Year.

1126
01:38:00,101 --> 01:38:03,102
If we ever meet again, by chance,

1127
01:38:05,621 --> 01:38:08,340
I think we will laugh ourselves
to death.

1128
01:38:09,781 --> 01:38:11,860
Well, it wasn't funny,

1129
01:38:12,101 --> 01:38:14,621
when I first saw you
sleeping on my sofa.

1130
01:38:15,501 --> 01:38:16,900
What about me?

1131
01:38:24,499 --> 01:38:28,499
Imagine me waking up at home

1132
01:38:28,740 --> 01:38:33,099
and seeing a strange woman,
who pours water over me.

1133
01:38:33,340 --> 01:38:36,338
And crying: "Get out of here!"

1134
01:38:36,580 --> 01:38:41,099
I cried back: "Get out yourself!"

1135
01:38:42,619 --> 01:38:45,338
I was so indignant,
I didn't know what to do.

1136
01:38:45,579 --> 01:38:47,578
Who is this man?

1137
01:38:48,458 --> 01:38:51,138
If he's a thief,
then why did he go to sleep?

1138
01:38:51,377 --> 01:38:56,657
He got tired and went to sleep
in the home, he had just robbed?

1139
01:38:57,858 --> 01:39:01,498
You know, I didn't like you at first.

1140
01:39:03,098 --> 01:39:07,737
And you looked utterly disgusting!

1141
01:39:12,857 --> 01:39:15,017
I can imagine!

1142
01:39:30,095 --> 01:39:31,335
Shall I open it?

