"No, I won't! You get out yourself!"

1153
01:40:30,720 --> 01:40:32,800
"Get out of my house!"

1154
01:40:34,960 --> 01:40:40,960
I was so indignant,
I didn't know what to do.

1155
01:40:41,480 --> 01:40:44,640
Who are you? If you're a thief,
then why did you go to sleep?

1156
01:40:44,960 --> 01:40:49,360
A thief that went to bed in the
house, he had just robbed?

1157
01:40:52,960 --> 01:40:57,080
You know, Nadya, I didn't like
you at first.

1158
01:40:57,320 --> 01:40:59,880
I really hated you!

1159
01:41:00,120 --> 01:41:05,720
And you looked disgusting!
Utterly disgusting!

1160
01:41:05,960 --> 01:41:08,880
I thought you were
a real termagant!

1161
01:41:53,800 --> 01:41:55,520
Nadya, forgive me.

1162
01:41:56,320 --> 01:41:59,320
I was wrong.
I got a little worked up.

1163
01:41:59,560 --> 01:42:03,080
It's OK. It's a good thing
you came back.

1164
01:42:03,320 --> 01:42:04,560
Really?

1165
01:42:06,560 --> 01:42:10,320
- Thank you.
- I thought you will never come back.

1166
01:42:10,560 --> 01:42:11,880
Let me take your coat.

1167
01:42:19,760 --> 01:42:21,000
Come in.

1168
01:42:29,080 --> 01:42:33,040
- He's still here?
- I couldn't turn him out into the cold!

1169
01:42:33,560 --> 01:42:35,800
The first flight is only
at 7 in the morning.

1170
01:42:36,080 --> 01:42:40,640
He could spend the night
at the airport. Not a big deal!

1171
01:42:42,720 --> 01:42:43,960
Sit down.

1172
01:42:45,400 --> 01:42:50,320
- I see you had dinner.
- Didn't make sense to stay hungry!

1173
01:42:50,560 --> 01:42:55,400
Music... Well that's cozy.
I like that!

1174
01:42:55,800 --> 01:42:58,240
- Why don't you join us?
- Join you? Thank you very much.

1175
01:42:58,480 --> 01:43:01,680
- Don't pick on words.
- Can I talk to you for a minute?

1176
01:43:01,920 --> 01:43:04,400
Please, just one minute.

1177
01:43:08,080 --> 01:43:11,720
Let's call a taxi and let him
bugger off to the airport.

1178
01:43:11,960 --> 01:43:17,160
On New Year's night a taxi
won't come before morning.

1179
01:43:17,400 --> 01:43:19,240
Then let him walk.

1180
01:43:19,480 --> 01:43:22,800
- Walk to the airport?
- Yes, walk to the airport.

1181
01:43:23,040 --> 01:43:24,040
So far away?

1182
01:43:24,280 --> 01:43:27,200
Now you're starting to feel
sorry for him.

1183
01:43:28,040 --> 01:43:31,960
Even my boundless patience
has its limits.

1184
01:43:32,200 --> 01:43:33,800
Mine too.

1185
01:43:34,720 --> 01:43:37,120
Maybe there was something
between you?

1186
01:43:37,480 --> 01:43:38,960
You ought to be ashamed of yourself!

1187
01:43:41,040 --> 01:43:43,720
I'm not talking to you!

1188
01:43:43,960 --> 01:43:47,160
If you love a woman,
you have to trust her.

1189
01:43:47,400 --> 01:43:49,280
Nadya, bring this character to order.

1190
01:43:49,520 --> 01:43:53,240
She is a wonderful woman.
As a person.

1191
01:43:53,480 --> 01:43:56,640
She is intelligent.
She cooks well. I ate!

1192
01:43:57,520 --> 01:44:01,680
Bring him to order,
or I don't know what I'll do!

1193
01:44:01,960 --> 01:44:05,720
She's tactful.
Above all, she's beautiful.

1194
01:44:05,960 --> 01:44:09,720
- I'll kill him!
- You have to apologize to her!

1195
01:44:09,960 --> 01:44:12,080
- What are you doing?
- And you?

1196
01:44:12,400 --> 01:44:13,840
Ippolit, stop it!

1197
01:44:14,080 --> 01:44:15,800
Bastard! I'll show you!

1198
01:44:18,400 --> 01:44:20,080
All I need is a fight here!

1199
01:44:20,320 --> 01:44:21,920
Apologize to her! You!

1200
01:44:22,160 --> 01:44:23,560
I can't stand familiarities!

1201
01:44:23,800 --> 01:44:25,080
You are defeated!

1202
01:44:25,320 --> 01:44:26,840
Zhenya, stop it!

1203
01:44:27,080 --> 01:44:29,560
We have to see, who's defeated
here! You'll break my arm!

1204
01:44:29,800 --> 01:44:32,080
I'll break it, I'll fix it!

1205
01:44:32,320 --> 01:44:34,240
- Zhenya!
- So he's already Zhenya for you!

1206
01:44:34,480 --> 01:44:37,120
What do you expect her to call me?
Vasya?

1207
01:44:37,360 --> 01:44:39,080
Let go of my arm!

1208
01:44:39,320 --> 01:44:41,040
Will you stop it!

1209
01:44:41,320 --> 01:44:42,560
Apologize!

1210
01:44:42,800 --> 01:44:44,320
That's enough!

1211
01:44:48,480 --> 01:44:49,840
Get off me.

1212
01:44:50,080 --> 01:44:52,040
I didn't want to beat him up.
He started it.

1213
01:44:53,760 --> 01:44:55,440
Now leave, both of you!

1214
01:44:56,160 --> 01:44:57,240
Both of you!

1215
01:45:00,720 --> 01:45:02,120
Well, if that's what you want!

1216
01:45:05,640 --> 01:45:09,440
I'll remember this New Year for
as long as I live.

1217
01:45:09,680 --> 01:45:13,440
Please do.
Do me a favor, try not to forget it.

1218
01:45:14,040 --> 01:45:17,840
- Please.
- No, no, after you.

1219
01:45:18,080 --> 01:45:21,240
- Be so kind as to leave here.
- I'm in no hurry.

1220
01:45:22,160 --> 01:45:24,440
Stop playing the clown!

1221
01:45:50,720 --> 01:45:53,800
Tanya, I'll come to your place.

1222
01:45:54,640 --> 01:45:57,600
No, nothing happened.

1223
01:45:59,800 --> 01:46:01,120
I'll explain later.

1224
01:46:04,800 --> 01:46:07,080
All right, then you drop by.

1225
01:46:15,680 --> 01:46:17,880
- Which way are you going?
- That way..

1226
01:46:18,160 --> 01:46:20,520
- Then I'm heading this way.
- We go in different directions.

1227
01:47:11,480 --> 01:47:13,440
- Well, well...
- She threw you out.

1228
01:47:14,000 --> 01:47:15,480
She threw both of us out.

1229
01:47:25,120 --> 01:47:28,720
Let's stay outside then.
I have plenty of time before my flight.

1230
01:47:29,040 --> 01:47:31,400
And today's my day off.

1231
01:47:39,320 --> 01:47:41,720
- Can't say it is warm.
- Yes, rather cool.

1232
01:47:42,560 --> 01:47:45,600
I've noticed, your underwear
is not fit for winter.

1233
01:47:46,240 --> 01:47:48,960
