farewell...

1234
01:47:49,800 --> 01:47:52,280
- Farewell?
- A lethal outcome.

1235
01:47:53,360 --> 01:47:55,760
And your boots have thin soles.

1236
01:47:56,040 --> 01:47:58,000
- So we'll die together then.
- I don't intend to die.

1237
01:47:58,280 --> 01:48:00,240
I can go sit in the car.

1238
01:48:06,440 --> 01:48:09,320
Ippolit Georgievich,
what are you thinking about?

1239
01:48:09,800 --> 01:48:12,560
I don't have to account
for my thoughts.

1240
01:48:12,840 --> 01:48:14,840
Somehow I can tell,
you're thinking about me.

1241
01:48:15,120 --> 01:48:17,400
Yes, I am thinking about you,
adventurer.

1242
01:48:17,640 --> 01:48:20,400
You have no respect for anything.

1243
01:48:20,680 --> 01:48:23,040
People like you always pry
into other people's affairs.

1244
01:48:23,320 --> 01:48:25,080
They believe in impulse,
not in common sense.

1245
01:48:25,360 --> 01:48:26,480
You are uncontrollable!

1246
01:48:27,560 --> 01:48:31,600
Your actions are guided not by
reason, but by unruly passions.

1247
01:48:31,880 --> 01:48:33,360
You constitute social danger.

1248
01:48:34,680 --> 01:48:37,280
What a flattering description.

1249
01:48:37,560 --> 01:48:40,680
- What are you thinking about?
- Hot tea.

1250
01:48:41,320 --> 01:48:44,600
How about frankness in exchange
for frankness.

1251
01:48:45,720 --> 01:48:47,120
All right.

1252
01:48:48,320 --> 01:48:50,720
People like you are always right,

1253
01:48:50,960 --> 01:48:53,480
because you live the right way.

1254
01:48:53,800 --> 01:48:55,040
According to instructions.

1255
01:48:55,280 --> 01:48:57,040
But that is your weak point.

1256
01:48:57,640 --> 01:49:01,280
You're not capable of acting on
an impulse or doing great things.

1257
01:49:01,520 --> 01:49:04,480
But you can't fit life into
a perfect scheme.

1258
01:49:18,800 --> 01:49:20,400
- That's it!
- What?

1259
01:49:20,640 --> 01:49:23,640
I have to return. I forgot my bag.

1260
01:49:23,880 --> 01:49:27,040
- You did that on purpose!
- Why did I have to freeze out here?

1261
01:49:27,280 --> 01:49:28,840
I'll get your bag for you.

