an expensive birch switch in it.

1263
01:49:32,120 --> 01:49:36,480
- Why did you go to the bath?
- You won't understand.

1264
01:49:42,360 --> 01:49:45,680
Hello! Moscow? Galya?

1265
01:49:46,360 --> 01:49:50,360
Yes. Can I speak with Lukashine?

1266
01:49:51,040 --> 01:49:52,960
He left for the airport.

1267
01:49:54,440 --> 01:49:55,920
Just a stranger.

1268
01:49:57,600 --> 01:50:00,120
Tell me, how did he end up
at your place?

1269
01:50:00,840 --> 01:50:03,280
I'll explain everything.

1270
01:50:04,040 --> 01:50:05,760
Last night Zhenya
went to a bathhouse.

1271
01:50:06,360 --> 01:50:12,320
What are you talking about?
He has a bath at home.

1272
01:50:13,520 --> 01:50:14,720
It's a tradition they have.

1273
01:50:15,760 --> 01:50:19,760
Every year he and his school
friends...

1274
01:50:34,360 --> 01:50:36,760
You've known each other for
many years?

1275
01:50:37,000 --> 01:50:40,440
No, we met several hours ago.

1276
01:50:40,680 --> 01:50:44,400
My home address
is the same as his in Moscow.

1277
01:50:44,640 --> 01:50:47,720
Apt. 12, 25, 3rd Constructors St.

1278
01:50:47,960 --> 01:50:50,440
And he came here thinking,
it was his home.

1279
01:50:51,040 --> 01:50:55,880
So you know his Moscow address.

1280
01:50:57,240 --> 01:50:58,640
Please...

1281
01:51:07,520 --> 01:51:08,960
Calm down.

1282
01:51:10,520 --> 01:51:12,160
Don't order me about.

1283
01:51:15,040 --> 01:51:17,600
- Let me help you.
- I don't want any help from you.

1284
01:51:22,600 --> 01:51:24,200
My hands are cold.

1285
01:51:27,120 --> 01:51:28,640
It's as simple as that.

1286
01:51:30,360 --> 01:51:31,360
You crook.

1287
01:51:34,120 --> 01:51:36,200
No, you got the wrong idea.

1288
01:51:36,480 --> 01:51:39,920
Galya, don't hang up, please.

1289
01:51:41,080 --> 01:51:44,080
Zhenya is a very good man,
a very kind one.

1290
01:51:45,280 --> 01:51:49,200
I must admit, I envy you, Galya.

1291
01:51:49,720 --> 01:51:51,640
Yes, I do like him a lot.

1292
01:51:51,920 --> 01:51:53,400
You must forgive him.

1293
01:52:09,040 --> 01:52:11,480
Why are you defending him?

1294
01:52:11,720 --> 01:52:12,880
Are you married?

1295
01:52:14,120 --> 01:52:16,040
What does that have to do with it?

1296
01:52:16,560 --> 01:52:18,360
You're not then.

1297
01:52:19,520 --> 01:52:22,760
So he flew to Leningrad
to see in the New Year with you.

1298
01:52:24,280 --> 01:52:27,120
- How old are you?
- Not very young.

1299
01:52:27,640 --> 01:52:31,040
- Your last chance?
- Aren't you ashamed of yourself?

1300
01:52:31,600 --> 01:52:33,000
Me? Ashamed?

1301
01:52:34,160 --> 01:52:35,880
I didn't steel your fiance.

1302
01:52:36,200 --> 01:52:40,440
Galya, you got it all wrong!

1303
01:52:40,880 --> 01:52:42,240
You are a vamp.

1304
01:52:43,760 --> 01:52:48,040
In the end at the last moment
he'll dump you too.

1305
01:53:14,720 --> 01:53:15,880
I'm sorry.

1306
01:53:17,120 --> 01:53:21,880
I'm terribly sorry, but I left
my bag with the birch switch.

1307
01:53:23,440 --> 01:53:24,800
Galya called.

1308
01:53:25,360 --> 01:53:26,520
Galya?

1309
01:53:28,760 --> 01:53:30,400
How did she find out the number?

1310
01:53:32,040 --> 01:53:38,040
Oh yes, I told her myself.
And you have a simple number.

1311
01:53:38,400 --> 01:53:41,960
I tried to explain everything,
but she didn't believe me.

1312
01:53:42,200 --> 01:53:44,920
I told her you left to the airport.

1313
01:53:48,120 --> 01:53:49,440
I see...

1314
01:53:51,640 --> 01:53:53,040
Yes, thank you.

1315
01:53:59,840 --> 01:54:00,960
Well, I'll be going now.

1316
01:54:02,880 --> 01:54:06,160
- Good luck.
- Thank you very much.

1317
01:54:11,600 --> 01:54:16,240
Once again sorry for the intrusion.

1318
01:54:18,520 --> 01:54:20,000
- Thank you.
- That was nothing.

1319
01:54:28,560 --> 01:54:30,160
I'm off...

1320
01:54:35,520 --> 01:54:37,720
I just wanted to say...

1321
01:54:38,280 --> 01:54:39,520
What?

1322
01:54:43,040 --> 01:54:44,840
Can I call you some time?

1323
01:54:47,440 --> 01:54:48,880
Do you remember my phone number?

1324
01:54:50,280 --> 01:54:52,080
14-50-30.

1325
01:54:53,800 --> 01:54:55,200
Call me.

1326
01:54:59,120 --> 01:55:01,080
- Happy New Year!
- Thank you.

1327
01:55:01,560 --> 01:55:04,720
- Happy New Year to you too.
- Thank you.

1328
01:55:08,480 --> 01:55:11,000
Well... I'm off.

1329
01:55:11,560 --> 01:55:15,880
But how will you get to the airport?

1330
01:55:18,760 --> 01:55:21,960
- Buses don't run yet.
- I'll get there somehow.

1331
01:55:23,600 --> 01:55:24,920
Go then.

