1387
02:00:24,240 --> 02:00:25,640
You're lying again?

1388
02:00:28,160 --> 02:00:29,400
Well, almost.

1389
02:00:38,320 --> 02:00:41,400
- Where do you work?
- At an outpatients clinic.

1390
02:00:42,160 --> 02:00:43,480
I receive patients.

1391
02:00:43,720 --> 02:00:46,000
Sometimes up to 30 a day.

1392
02:00:47,720 --> 02:00:49,040
Do you ever get tired?

1393
02:00:49,600 --> 02:00:53,680
Of course. But they're in pain,
and they need help.

1394
02:00:55,720 --> 02:00:57,560
All right, I will sing for you.

1395
02:00:58,160 --> 02:01:00,840
