with a suffocating wave

1404
02:01:53,720 --> 02:01:57,840
When slightly brushing
sleeves with you.

1405
02:02:00,480 --> 02:02:03,960
I thank you
from the bottom of my heart

1406
02:02:04,480 --> 02:02:08,800
For loving me so,
without knowing it.

1407
02:02:10,600 --> 02:02:12,120
For my quiet nights,

1408
02:02:12,800 --> 02:02:15,840
For the scarcity of our encounters
in the hours of dawn,

1409
02:02:16,120 --> 02:02:21,760
For the moon and the sun
not shining above our heads,

1410
02:02:22,880 --> 02:02:27,600
For you being in love, alas,
with someone else,

1411
02:02:30,120 --> 02:02:34,800
For me being in love, alas,
