02:59:29,400 --> 02:59:30,520
Wish you all the best!

2032
02:59:30,760 --> 02:59:31,880
Where is he?

2033
02:59:32,120 --> 02:59:33,680
Wake him up.

2034
02:59:39,960 --> 02:59:41,320
Hello.

2035
02:59:42,520 --> 02:59:45,920
How could I have made such a
blunder? I never ever get drunk.

2036
02:59:47,840 --> 02:59:51,800
I'm happy to see,
that you, Zhenya, and...

2037
02:59:53,280 --> 02:59:54,360
Galya.

2038
02:59:54,600 --> 02:59:58,360
That we are your friends
and Galya has forgiven you.

2039
02:59:58,600 --> 03:00:00,680
Zhenya, quit kissing around.

2040
03:00:01,440 --> 03:00:05,640
We can't. We've missed
each other so much.

2041
03:00:06,200 --> 03:00:09,440
I don't care if they kiss. Do you?
Do you feel uneasy? Not me.

2042
03:00:09,680 --> 03:00:12,600
Zhenya, we are happy
that Galya has forgiven you.

2043
03:00:12,840 --> 03:00:16,720
We are happy,
that you and Galya have reunited.

2044
03:00:19,880 --> 03:00:21,120
Mother!

2045
03:00:23,560 --> 03:00:25,640
My Nadya has come.

2046
03:00:37,040 --> 03:00:40,680
You think I am light-headed?

2047
03:00:42,040 --> 03:00:43,520
We shall wait and see.

2048
03:00:46,440 --> 03:00:50,440
- Do you understand what's going on?
- Are you asking me?

2049
03:00:51,440 --> 03:00:54,520
I have a feeling this is not Galya.

2050
03:00:57,120 --> 03:01:01,120
Well say something.
You're the most quick-witted of all.

2051
03:01:01,800 --> 03:01:05,640
I can say for sure
that one of them is Zhenya.

2052
03:01:07,120 --> 03:01:08,520
Friends!

2053
03:01:10,720 --> 03:01:14,760
I am grateful to you
for changing my life.

2054
03:01:15,600 --> 03:01:18,600
I am grateful that fate
lead me to Leningrad.

2055
03:01:20,000 --> 03:01:24,960
And that in Leningrad
there is a street of the same name, a house

2056
03:01:25,840 --> 03:01:27,400
just like mine
and an apartment just like mine.

2057
03:01:30,200 --> 03:01:32,600
Otherwise I would never be happy.

2058
03:01:32,840 --> 03:01:35,120
We would never be happy.

2059
03:01:36,280 --> 03:01:38,920
We would never be happy.

2060
03:01:44,080 --> 03:01:47,120
I asked the ash-tree:

2061
03:01:48,200 --> 03:01:50,560
Where is my loved one?

